Written by Chulwoo Pack (chulwoo.pack@gmail.com)

This repo contains document image binarization code (sauvola) in python.


1. How to Use
  (1) To get simple binarization result:
     python binarization [folder-path containing images]
  (2) To apply mophological transformation first and get the binarization result:
     python binarization_morphological [folder-path containing images]

